Africa will host it 's first NBA match with basketball stars Chris Paul and Luol Deng .
The August 1 encounter will feature a Team Africa vs Team World format at the iconic Ellis Park Stadium in Johannesburg , South Africa .
Team Africa will be comprised of players from the continent and of second generation while Team World will consist of those from the rest of the globe .
The game will take place following the 13th edition of Basketball without Borders Africa .